When the user clicks Submit Query, the web application makes the following GET request to the server.

This example is a reflected HTML injection because the user sent JavaScript in an HTTP
request and the web application  responded the exact sameJavaScript.

To execute this script, any user needs only click the following link:

http://publicpages.targetwebsite.com/~someuser/LearningPhp.php?input=<script>alert(1)

</script>

